# 9. 凡人の絵

Kanade: Yuki, wait!
Kanade: Huh? I'm back in my room?
Ena: <K! K, answer me! Kanade, are you okay?!>
Mizuki: <K, are you there?! Please say something!>
Kanade: <You guys?>
Ena: <K! Oh, I'm so glad!>
Mizuki: <Phew... It looks like we all made it back okay. That's a relief.>
Ena: <What exactly just happened to us? As soon as Miku touched me, I was back in my room.>
Mizuki: <And what was that SEKAI place? Miku and Yuki were both acting so strange.>
???: Be honest, K, Enanan, Amia... You all want to disappear more than anyone.
Ena: <Seriously, what's up with Yuki?>
Ena: <Hiding the fact that she was OWN and laughing at us behind our backs!>
Ena: <I feel like an idiot for saying how great she was like that!>
Mizuki: <W-Well, we don't exactly know if she was doing it to be mean. Still...>
Mizuki: <Yuki sure is a lot different than I thought.>
Mizuki: <I guess you can never tell what someone's really like over voice chat, huh? Haha.>
Ena: <I don't see what's funny about this.>
Mizuki: <So what do we do now? After that, I don't think Yuki is going to be coming back.>
Kanade: <.....>
Kanade: <I wasn't good enough...>
Ena: <Huh? Did you say something, K?>
Kanade: <It's nothing.>
Mizuki: <Maybe we should call it a night. I think we're all a little worn out.>
Mizuki: <We can talk more about Yuki and what we're going to do from here on out tomorrow.>
Ena: <I don't see any reason to talk about her after this. She basically said she wants to work alone. It's not like she's coming back!>
Ena: <If she can make songs like that all on her own, then...>
Mizuki: <Come on, let's talk about it later once we've all had some time to cool off. See you tomorrow♪>
Kanade: <.....>
???: K, the first time I heard your songs, I felt like they had saved me. A little bit.
???: But it wasn't enough. I wasn't able to find anything.
Kanade: <Sorry, I'm logging off too.>
Ena: <Ah...>
Ena: .....
???: I didn't see any reason to tell you, so I didn't.
???: I've never spoken to you as anyone other than Yuki, after all.
Ena: Hmph. What's with her?
Ena: Now that she can write songs like that by herself, she just doesn't care about us normies anymore, is that it?
Ena: She gets 200,000 views on her own, and then decides she doesn't need us?
[Yuki]: <It felt delicate and gentle, but also a little sad. I thought it was wonderful.>
[Enanan]: <Really?>
[Yuki]: <Yeah. I really like your art.>
[Enanan]: <Thanks, Yuki...>
Ena: How dare she...make fun of me like that...
Ena: She never cared for my art one bit!
Ena: .....
Ena: I'll show her! I'll keep drawing until I become bigger than her, then I can pay her back for making me look stupid!
Ena: This is terrible. The draft looked just fine, but now the perspective is all wrong.
Ena: I just can't get it to work.
Ena: This isn't good enough... No matter what I do...
???: Ena, you're still up?
Ena: Wha—
Ena: What are you doing? You think it's okay to barge into my room whenever you want, Dad?!
Ena's Father: I just thought you'd fallen asleep with the light on.
Ena's Father: What are you doing up so late? Were you drawing again?
Ena: What if I am?
Ena: Does it upset the genius artist when his talentless daughter draws?
Ena's Father: No. Do whatever you want.
Ena's Father: Anyone can draw. There's no rule that says you need to have talent to do it.
Ena: Just get out!
Ena: Why?! Why?!
Ena: Why is it that all these people with talent think it's okay to belittle me!
Ena: Making me look like an idiot!
Akito: Ena, it's the middle of the night. Keep it down, will ya? This about Dad again?
Ena: Shut up! This has nothing to do with you, Akito! Get out!
Akito: Yeah, whatever. You're the one who needs to shut up, though.
Akito: Draw as much as you like, but you need to sleep too.
Ena: *Huff*... *Huff*...
Ena: I have to keep drawing! I have to keep drawing! If I keep drawing, then even I could...
Ena: Even I... Even I could...
Ena: Can... Can I...
Ena: Can I really make something as good as...that?
Ena: I...
Ena: Hashtag whatever...hashtag spontaneous...
Social Media Comment: <Enanan, you're as cute as ever today!>
Social Media Comment: <So. Cute.>
Social Media Comment: <You're so beautiful I actually said it out loud!>
Ena: Haha. People are already commenting.
Ena: It's so easy to get people to notice me.
Ena: .....
Ena: But who cares... Why can't I...
Ena: I need to draw, but I just...
Ena: Why do things have to be like this?
???: You all want to disappear more than anyone.
Ena: She's right. I just want to disappear forever.
Ena: Why does the one who understands me have to be her?
